2009-06-25 10:47  xavier

	* [r5633] m4/acx.m4, m4/fc_integer.m4: Now octopus can be cross
	  compiled. To do it,
	  he user has to pass two variables
	  to the configure script:
	  
	  FC_INTEGER_SIZE=4
	  CC_FORTRAN_INT=int
	  
	  With this change octopus compiles in a Blue Gene/P.

